join(bytes,uint256,uint256).notice: method that allows a validator to join the subnet.         If the total confirmed collateral of the subnet is greater         or equal to minimum activation collateral as a result of this operation,         then  subnet will be registered.

kill().notice: method that allows to kill the subnet when all validators left.

leave().notice: method that allows a validator to leave the subnet.

preFund(uint256).notice: method to add some initial balance into a subnet that hasn't yet bootstrapped.

preRelease(uint256).notice: method to remove funds from the initial balance of a subnet.

setFederatedPower(address[],bytes[],uint.notice: Sets the federated power of validators.

stake(uint256).notice: method that allows a validator to increase its stake.         If the total confirmed collateral of the subnet is greater         or equal to minimum activation collateral as a result of this operation,         then  subnet will be registered.

stakeStorage(uint256).notice: method that allows a validator to increase its storage commited by amount.

unstake(uint256).notice: method that allows a validator to unstake a part of its collateral from a subnet.

unstakeStorage(uint256).notice: method that allows a validator to unstake a part of its storage from a subnet.
